His Guardian article is headlined “Ilhan Omar has become the target of a dangerous hate campaign.” Bayoumi is an English professor at Brooklyn College at the City University of New York.
REP. ILHAN OMAR: Far too long, we have lived with the discomfort of being a second-class citizen.
This is the argument you make in your piece, “Ilhan Omar has become the target of a dangerous hate campaign.” Give us a few quotes.
What we saw with Nancy Pelosi’s statement, for example, on Ilhan Omar was, I thought, extremely disappointing.
I mean, does that mean that Ilhan Omar can only criticize Ilhan Omar?